p10 = [[Singles match]] for the [[WWE Championship]]<ref name=BSMATCH>{{cite web|last1=Benigno|first1=Anthony|title=WWE Champion Drew McIntyre def. Big Show|url=https://www.wwe.com/shows/raw/2020-04-06#full-detail-40075497|work=WWE|date=April 6, 2020|accessdate=April 6, 2020}}</ref>\n|time10 = 6:55<ref name=BSTIME>{{Cite web|url=https://prowrestling.net/site/2020/04/06/4-6-wwe-raw-results-powells-live-review-of-the-night-after-wrestlemania-36-edition-featuring-new-wwe-champion-drew-mcintyre-whats-next-for-edge-seth-rollins-becky-lynch-and-shayna-baszler/|title=4/6 WWE Raw Results: Powell\u2019s live review of the night after WrestleMania 36 edition featuring new WWE Champion Drew McIntyre, what\u2019s next for Edge, Seth Rollins, Becky Lynch, and Shayna Baszler|last=Powell|first=Jason|date=April 6, 2020|website=ProWrestling.net|publisher=Last Row Media|access-date=April 7, 2020}}</ref>\n}}\n=== SmackDown Women's Championship Fatal 5-Way match eliminations===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!Eliminated\n!Wrestler\n!Eliminated by\n!Method\n!Time<ref name=\"WM36Part2\"/>\n|-\n|1\n|[[Tamina Snuka|Tamina]]\n|[[Bayley (wrestler)|Bayley]], [[Lacey Evans]], [[Naomi (wrestler)|Naomi]], and [[Sasha Banks]]\n|Pinfall\n|6:35\n|-\n|2\n|[[Naomi (wrestler)|Naomi]]\n|[[Sasha Banks]]\n|Submission\n|10:20\n|-\n|3\n|[[Sasha Banks]]\n|[[Lacey Evans]]\n|Pinfall\n|13:25\n|-\n|4\n|[[Lacey Evans]]\n|[[Bayley (wrestler)|Bayley]]\n|Pinfall\n|19:20\n|-\n|'''Winner'''\n|'''[[Bayley (wrestler)|Bayley]] (c)'''\n|colspan=3 {{NA}}\n|-\n|}\n\n==Notes==\n{{reflist|group=Note}}\n{{notelist}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Official website|https://www.wwe.com/shows/wrestlemania|WrestleMania official website}}\n\n{{2020 WWE Network events}}\n{{WWEPPV|WrestleMania}}\n\n[[Category:2020 WWE Network events]]\n[[Category:2020 WWE pay-per-view events]]\n[[Category:2020 in Florida]]\n[[Category:Professional wrestling in Orlando, Florida]]\n[[Category:Events in Orlando, Florida]]\n[